    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vertical supports for a piece of furniture, typically used for longer supports of modified cylindrical, columnar, or pier-like form. For shorter vertical supports, use "feet (object components)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
